

Main screen
Mapbox map
Bottom Nav

During Run:
    Play/Pause/Stop button
    Display:
        1. duration
        2. current time
        3. mile splits
        4. distance
        5. route line

Save route on finishing
Plan a run -> round trip or not
Choose music maybe playlist during run

5 options of run/walk:
1. Quick start
2. Plan a Run
3. Run for time
4. Run for duration
5. Race yourself - Run a previous route for time

Save for user:
    Total distance
    Total time
    # of runs
    average mile split

Save for each run:
    Route line
    distance
    time
    avg mile split
    each mile splits

My Runs - Save a list of every run completed
My Achievements - Longest timed run, Furthest run, best mile split, best run (by mile split), overall times and mileage, and mile split
Settings - Toggle voiceover, music, current run info voiceover, metric/imperial, see Mapbox API calls (secret menu)